    "description": "Jungle Lodges Karnataka Global Group is actively seeking a talented and motivated Guest Relations Manager to join our dynamic team in Nashik. This is an excellent opportunity for professionals who are passionate about making a real impact in a fast-growing organization.\n\nAbout Jungle Lodges Karnataka Global Group:\nJungle Lodges Karnataka Global Group is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Develop and maintain relationships with corporate clients\n• Deliver exceptional guest experiences in line with brand standards\n• Manage reservations and optimize room revenue through yield management\n• Coordinate with travel agents and OTAs for occupancy optimization\n• Prepare daily operating reports and present to management\n• Ensure compliance with FSSAI, health, and safety regulations\n• Handle guest complaints and resolve issues promptly\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Tech / B.E. in Computer Science or related discipline\n• 3-6 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Hotel Management\n• Proficiency in MICE\n• Proficiency in GDS Systems\n• Proficiency in Sommelier Skills\n• Proficiency in Opera PMS\n• Proficiency in Travel Management\n• Proficiency in Food Safety\n• Proficiency in Front Office\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Flexible working hours\n• Life and accident insurance\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Referral bonus program\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 7 LPA - 15 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Nashik, Maharashtra, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Jungle Lodges Karnataka Global Group!",
